{"tid":815782,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《中國新說唱》吳亦凡不停「Skr Skr」，究竟Skr是什麼意思？","createTime":"2018-09-12T09:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T10:17:05.000Z","uid":197813,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15d8013ffaad6db4edfe75f301e4a91b2e94c04a","tid":815782,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"最新一季的《中國新說唱》已經播放到第二季，大家還記得吳亦凡在《中國有嘻哈》中經常說的那句「你有Freestyle嗎？」新的一季，新的口頭禪也同時推出，這次充滿魔性的口頭禪就「Skr ～Skr～」，究竟這是甚麼意思呢？<br />\n<br />\n吳亦凡在前一季的《中國有嘻哈》不停問人「你有Freestyle嗎？」成為了當時的網絡潮語。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/174944_d66cf5e58c8fae4ba91d72b54658fea6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F174944_d66cf5e58c8fae4ba91d72b54658fea6.jpg&h=c6d8d6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/174944_46b1c52c60a9fed9a9a6a609e3502f76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F174944_46b1c52c60a9fed9a9a6a609e3502f76.png&h=cfc401a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳亦凡在最新一季的《中國新說唱》中不斷展現了他最新的口頭禪「Skr～Skr～」，尤其是成長選手的時候，最後都會有這一句，「Skr Skr」，這句充滿魔性的句子，真的十分洗腦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/175235_899bde75502be1aeeebc33f2d99682ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F175235_899bde75502be1aeeebc33f2d99682ca.jpg&h=2beb57ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Skr Skr」究竟是甚麼意思呢？網上主要流傳有3種意思，一種是在擁有跑車元素的饒舌歌中表達車輪與地摩擦的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n一種是在表達不認同。<br />\n<br />\n還有一種是表達厲害、「屈機」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/175200_b9b158ba4f3443965dd9aba1ea2955f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F175200_b9b158ba4f3443965dd9aba1ea2955f1.jpg&h=70dba9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/175200_a1ae0f811e566c7f7ab23c8729392da5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F175200_a1ae0f811e566c7f7ab23c8729392da5.jpg&h=c7f96dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有望掛八號，skr skr🤙🤙"},{"pid":"7fcdfa6ceb5bbcd82958f74c757cd0860d9588d8","tid":815782,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">車輪與地摩擦的聲音</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咩車摩咩地可以發出skr skr"},{"pid":"04c685c2484d5ed926c282385cb8501af138182f","tid":815782,"uid":197813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fcdfa6ceb5bbcd82958f74c757cd0860d9588d8","tid":815782,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">車輪與地摩擦的聲音</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咩車摩咩地可以發出skr skr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"急剎咪會skr"},{"pid":"5e6547dd1292b4e1b60a376d33ee6d36c2b50e6e","tid":815782,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"你有freestyle嘛？"},{"pid":"abbfc8faece9496f74c4f95933109dcba3a6a095","tid":815782,"uid":84633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"點發音"},{"pid":"8003d1a85a4121b8c3ae6869c425fe94846fc79d","tid":815782,"uid":29040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"其實點讀 skr?"},{"pid":"87fa3bafebaed8ed35a566c683a422c850257c8b","tid":815782,"uid":23801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"最新一季的《中國新說唱》已經播放到第二季<br />\n咁樣又係咩意思"},{"pid":"3ab253f7f1d2f63b44f3d1a1e50f2b5ee096d312","tid":815782,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/181704_569d423d85c85cdd81e274896deed928.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F181704_569d423d85c85cdd81e274896deed928.png&h=c241d056&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}